{"tid":2318150,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呃9人傳銷奶粉","createTime":"2020-12-09T06:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T19:05:04.000Z","uid":118988,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"bbc5eb7cefd69674075398355ec8a56d84100d4b","tid":2318150,"uid":118988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T06:20:46.000Z","msg":"代友貼文︰<br />\n各位好，我叫laughing gor，係反亮碧思傳銷telegram 群組新任版主，由於我冇ISP mail，所以申請唔到連登account ，唯有借用老友account po文，請多多包涵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講下一隻亮碧產品:monb&eacute;lac夢貝朗<br />\n<br />\n亮狗成日話依隻奶粉幾好幾好，又promo一隻傳銷雞做*奶粉博士<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/682880877713424384/786103151475949614/Screenshot_20201208-195947_Chrome.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F682880877713424384%2F786103151475949614%2FScreenshot_20201208-195947_Chrome.jpg&h=4ef02bae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/682880877713424384/786103165828333578/Screenshot_20201208-200000_Chrome.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F682880877713424384%2F786103165828333578%2FScreenshot_20201208-200000_Chrome.jpg&h=a8115dc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又話依隻奶粉係歐盟認證又乜又柒，又話係「法國製造」<br />\n咁啱有手足又打開online game又識法國人喎，咁.....佢咪問個法國朋友有冇依隻產品囉<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/682880877713424384/786102900874936370/IMG_20201208_195243_087.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F682880877713424384%2F786102900874936370%2FIMG_20201208_195243_087.jpg&h=feafc95b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/682880877713424384/786102961704534016/IMG_20201208_195252_438.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F682880877713424384%2F786102961704534016%2FIMG_20201208_195252_438.jpg&h=a4bce414&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/682880877713424384/786102997666627595/IMG_20201208_195258_736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F682880877713424384%2F786102997666627595%2FIMG_20201208_195258_736.jpg&h=31d173ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/682880877713424384/786103029107392532/IMG_20201208_195255_924.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F682880877713424384%2F786103029107392532%2FIMG_20201208_195255_924.jpg&h=d2642471&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/682880877713424384/786103088460202044/IMG_20201208_195303_181.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F682880877713424384%2F786103088460202044%2FIMG_20201208_195303_181.jpg&h=040d2dde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嗱!cap圖有哂，唔識英文唔緊要，我依家翻譯<br />\n<br />\n手足:可唔可以去supermarket奶粉區影下有冇依隻野？<br />\n<br />\n法國佬:我好肯定好肯定咁話俾你知，我從未見過，我平時用好多時間响supermarket，你懂的<br />\n<br />\n法國佬:而且佢個label都唔係法文，亂砌出嚟嘅，點會有得賣？<br />\n<br />\n手足:咁&hellip;&hellip;monb&eacute;lac到底係咪意思？可唔可以強行英譯？<br />\n<br />\n法國佬:個字亂砌出嚟點譯？<br />\n<br />\n手足:等於啲鬼佬紋中文响身唔知紋乜鳩咁解？<br />\n<br />\n法國佬:係呀！lol<br />\n<br />\n即係話:即係法國奶粉「夢貝朗」係一隻法國冇得賣嘅產品&hellip;&hellip;即係乜鳩都呃人啦<br />\n<br />\n今次講住咁多先，下次介紹下亮碧狗上一隻沙門氏菌超標嘅奶粉 : 不能食用的「維達寶」<br />\n<br />\n唉！楊成文老千，你拍心口話要將夢貝朗發展成hk no.1奶粉，隻奶粉來歷不明，又貴，又唔俾經銷商賣貨(參見經銷商守則)，咁點姐？夾硬塞俾水魚餵仔？有冇毒架？呃完人連人哋細路都唔放過要毒鳩人？<br />\n<br />\n註:所謂嘅奶粉博士，畢業於Honolulu University(檀香山大學)，五大垃圾學校之一，係美國大學但係論文係用中文寫🙈<br />\n奶粉博士？叫你傳銷博士好似適合啲喎<br />\n<br />\n以下係&quot;奶粉博士&quot;Rubie係怡安閣(第三波疫情傳銷群組)嘅自我介紹：<br />\n各位董事長，領導，您好！&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n🐰我叫Rubie (露比) ，香港人。<br />\n👥 貴人Miya領導，對上Marshal董，Agnes董，賢董。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n2019年4月經貴人接觸SG平台，最初純粹因想識人而到公司了解並加盟，加盟一個月時間把公司產品全面分析，對公司產品非常有信心👍🏻繼而放棄醫科學位 以41%全職發展。<br />\n💰20% 38% 41% 自己儲蓄<br />\n💪🏻強項：<br />\n* 產品（保健品, 粉奶, 醫美)<br />\n* 供應商實力<br />\n* 家長<br />\n<br />\n亮碧思傳銷老千為禍香港22年，一代又一代嘅後生仔俾班陰毒老千害到負債<br />\n亮碧思/Francine/BV百麗/Svi詩貝朗背後都係同一個老闆，叫黃樹雄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/682880877713424384/786105494929801216/IMG_20200820_011321_084.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F682880877713424384%2F786105494929801216%2FIMG_20200820_011321_084.jpg&h=2ad4f750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而爆肺炎群組嘅star global群組，就係黄樹雄隻「頭馬」:楊成文<br />\n<br />\n到底香港人要俾佢哋呃多幾多年先醒覺？政府唔立法杜絕傳銷老鼠屎，個責任到底晌市民定政府身上<br />\n<br />\n我哋已經不期望政府會做嘢保障市民財產(香港冇集體訴訟，水魚俾人呃完上天無路落地無門)，香港人你已經得翻條底褲，你自己唔桿衛自己財產，你連條底褲都冇埋<br />\n<br />\n請加入反亮碧詩大聯盟<br />\nFacebook : （新Fb page） <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/304654040971216/?ref=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F304654040971216%2F%3Fref%3Dshare&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUIVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=b26a920c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/304654040971216/?ref=share</a><br />\n<br />\nTelegram :&nbsp;<br />\n@becareful_LB_Laminated_marketing<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一齊打巢亮狗，Happy歸零"},{"pid":"889acdf7a2fcabf640d48a2bd57dc11c7d78778b","tid":2318150,"uid":118988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T06:25:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9d2eba078c649da0b08895bcc8abe3fb564ecf0","tid":2318150,"uid":118988,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T06:30:45.000Z","msg":"不要再讓亮狗呃人錢"},{"pid":"1f6f52a46e865ada5f0c9f90327a1e96fb81f7ab","tid":2318150,"uid":3063,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a9d2eba078c649da0b08895bcc8abe3fb564ecf0","tid":2318150,"uid":118988,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T06:30:45.000Z","msg":"不要再讓亮狗呃人錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T06:34:00.000Z","msg":"今時今日都仲中招既<br />\n要驗驗智商"},{"pid":"671ee80d0ceb2952447f4199c45e738e9